'''库仑爆炸'''是从强[[电磁场|电磁场]]耦合电子激发能到原子运动的一种现象。有着相同[[电荷|电荷]]的粒子的库仑斥力可以断裂维持固体的键（力）。当窄激光束照射上去时，小量的金属爆炸为被电离的原子微粒[[等离子体|等离子体]]。与热的烧蚀不同，库仑爆炸是“冷”的——在热量传导到足够远时，爆炸已完成了。

[[File:Bucky1.gif|thumb]]

库仑爆炸的蚀刻可以被用于任何材料来钻孔、去除表面层和表面结构化、表面微构化，如在打印过程中控制墨水的加载。<ref>{{cite journal |first= D. |last= Mëller |title= Picosecond Lasers for High-Quality Industrial Micromachining |journal= [[Photonics_Spectra|Photonics Spectra]] |date= November 2009 |pages= 46–47 |url= http://www.photonics.com/Article.aspx?AID=40296 |access-date= 2015-02-05 |archive-date= 2015-02-05 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20150205064043/http://www.photonics.com/Article.aspx?AID=40296 |dead-url= no }}</ref>

高速摄像机拍下了[[碱金属|碱金属]]在水中爆炸的过程，它被认为是库仑爆炸。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.nature.com/nchem/journal/vaop/ncurrent/full/nchem.2161.html|title=Coulomb explosion during the early stages of the reaction of alkali metals with water|work=Nature Chemistry|doi=10.1038/nchem.2161|date=26 Jan 2015}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.scientificamerican.com/article/sodium-s-explosive-secrets-revealed1/|work=Scientific American|date=27 Jan 2015|title=Sodium's Explosive Secrets Revealed|accessdate=2015-02-05|archive-date=2017-07-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170731210832/https://www.scientificamerican.com/article/sodium-s-explosive-secrets-revealed1/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

